  • public class DegreeSelect
extends java.lang.Object
    The class biasRandomWalk implements the baseline algorithm. In this very basic and simple algorithm we select the prominent nodes based on two criterion: Closeness measure Degree measure The performance/results of this algorithm are used to quantify any added value of the more complex algorithms.
